          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Halo fans can get massive limited-time discounts on <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0CBNSK6DY,B0BBSQQNF9,B0CJTBCPK3,B08V3GYR5S,B0BBSVQYPB,B0CMFF6WVG,B0BBSTM7H1,B09NZ515FM,B09NZRDDKD,B08J4J2KQ5,B0BBSTTJXX,B0CJG32PQZ&amp;tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">multiple officially licensed Mega Bloks building sets</a> themed around the video game series. The most notable deal is the popular <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors/dp/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">343 Guilty Spark display model</a> for $29.10 (was $70.19). The 609-piece set is part of Mega Bloks' collector series for adults. Amazon also a limited-time deal on the 635-piece <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive/dp/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Floodgate Firefight playset</a> that drops the price to $39.20 (was $75). Based on Halo 3, Floodgate Firefight is one of several Mega Halo building sets exclusive to Amazon.</p><div title="6537177 - Mega Bloks Halo Guilty Spark Deal" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="5370" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6537177 - Mega Bloks Halo Guilty Spark Deal" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors/dp/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors\/dp\/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors/dp/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Mega Bloks Halo Guilty Spark (609 pieces)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors/dp/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors\/dp\/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Replica-Building-Guilty-Display-Collectors/dp/B0CBNSK6DY?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$29.10 (was $70.19)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Based on the Monitor (AI robot) from Bungie's original Halo trilogy, the 609-piece replica of 343 Guilty Spark has cool interactive features that longtime fans will appreciate.</p><p>Spark has working LED lights with two display modes and a built-in speaker that plays 15 quotes from Halo: Combat Evolved, Halo 2, and Halo 3. The dialogue is voiced by the character's original actor Tim Dadabo. You can activate the lighting and audio features by pressing Spark's eye. The model is powered by three AAA batteries, which are included with the kit.</p><p>Guilty Spark comes with a buildable display stand and a name placard to attach to the base. The faithfully designed model measures 6.1 x 5.5 x 8 inches when connected to the stand.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive/dp/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive\/dp\/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive/dp/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Mega Bloks Halo Floodgate Firefight (635 pieces)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive/dp/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive\/dp\/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Floodgate-Firefight-Amazon-Exclusive/dp/B0BBSQQNF9?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$39.20 (was $75) | Amazon Exclusive</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Floodgate Firefight is a 635-piece playset recommended for builders ages 13 and up. As mentioned, it's exclusive to Amazon and on sale for $39.20, which is close to the all-time best price. The set originally retailed for $75, but lately it has hovered around $52.</p><p>The Halo 3-inspired building set has a modular design with four different layouts and multiple interactive features, including a working winch to move a storage crate across the map.</p><p>The set comes with micro action figures of Master Chief and three enemies and buildable accessories such as a forklift and crane. The posable figures can wield various weapons and other small accessories.</p></div>                      </div>   </div><hr><h2>More Halo Mega Bloks &amp; Mega Construx Sets</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4629799-halomegaconstrux.png" data-ref-id="1300-4629799" data-ratio="0.45217391304348" data-width="1150" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4629799-halomegaconstrux.png" data-ref-id="1300-4629799"></a><figcaption>Amazon-exclusive Mega Construx Halo micro figure sets</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4629799-halomegaconstrux.png"></figure><p>Amazon has <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0CBNSK6DY,B0BBSQQNF9,B0CJTBCPK3,B08V3GYR5S,B0BBSVQYPB,B0CMFF6WVG,B0BBSTM7H1,B09NZ515FM,B09NZRDDKD,B08J4J2KQ5,B0BBSTTJXX,B0CJG32PQZ&amp;tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">a bunch of other Halo Mega Bloks/Construx building sets</a> in stock right now. None of the others are on sale for as large of discounts, but you can save on a few other Amazon-exclusive products. The <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Building-Character-Articulation-Collectible/dp/B0CJTBCPK3?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Halo 2 Character Pack</a></strong> is on sale for $39.69 (was $54). This micro figure bundle is consistently one of the most popular Halo Mega Bloks products on Amazon. Along with 20 articulated character figures, the 338-piece set comes with swappable armor, weapons, and other small accessories. The <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Construx-Anniversary-Character-Exclusive/dp/B08V3GYR5S?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Halo 20th Anniversary Character Pack</a></strong>, though not on sale, is also exclusive to Amazon and comes with 20 micro figures for $54.</p><p>Other deals include the 469-piece <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Building-FLEETCOM-Warthog-Poseable-Accessories/dp/B0BBSTM7H1?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Fleetcom Warthog</a></strong> playset with five micro figures for $37.80 (was $45) and the 123-piece <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Construx-Hijacked-Infinite-Construction/dp/B08J4J2KQ5?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Hijacked Ghost</a></strong> with four figures for $23 (was $35).</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Building-Character-Articulation-Collectible/dp/B0CJTBCPK3?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Halo 2 Character Pack (338 pieces)</a> -- $39.69 (<del>$54</del>)</li><li><a href=